fields.text:
You scored a total of {{paq_total|apnumber}} on this questionnaire.

Your total asthma symptoms score was: {{paq_asthma|apnumber}}

Your total treatment burden score was: {{paq_burden|apnumber}}

## The total score on the LINQ is:  {{scores.linq.score}}


{% if scores.linq.score > 5 %}
This patient may require significant clarifications in numerous areas.
{% endif %}


<hr>


### Disease knowledge score: {{scores.linq_disease.score}}

{% if scores.linq_disease.score == 0 %}
The patient is fully informed
{% elif scores.linq_disease.score == 1  %}
The patient is reasonably well informed but could do with additional advice
{% else %}
<div class="text">
The patient would benefit from more information about their disease
</div>
{%endif%}






### Self management score: {{scores.linq_selfmanagement.score}}

{% if not answers.linq_whenabulance == "1" %}
<div class="text-warning">The patient may require clarification on when to call an abulance</div>
{%endif%}


### Medicines score: {{scores.linq_medicine.score}}

{% if scores.linq_medicine.score > 0 %}
<div class="text">The patient may benefit from advice regarding their medication</div>
{% else %}
The patient is fully informed.
{%endif%}


### Exercise score: {{scores.linq_exercise.score}}

{% if scores.linq_exercise.score > 0 %}
<div class="text">The patient may benefit from advice regarding exercise</div>
{% else %}
The patient is fully informed.
{%endif%}






### Smoking score: {{scores.linq_smoking.score}}

{% if answers.linq_smoker == 2 %}
<div class="text-warning">The patient still smokes</div>
{%endif%}


<!--
<hr>
<pre>
{{scores}}

{{answers}}

</pre>
-->

The patient's total Dose Index is **{{scores.dose.score|apnumber}}**. 

{% if answers.dose_mrc > 0 %}- <span class="text-info">Pulmonary rehabilitation</span> is indicated, based on the patient's MRC Dyspnoea score{%endif%}

{% if answers.dose_mrc > 0 %}- <span class="text-info">Long acting broncodilators</span>  are also indicated based on the patients dyspnoea score.{% endif %}

{% if answers.dose_exacerbations > 0 and  answers.dose_fev1 > 0 %}- <span class="text-info">Inhaled corticosteroids</span>  are indicated, based on the occurence of exacerbations and the patient's airway restriction.{%endif%}

{% if answers.dose_smokes > 0 %}- <span class="text-info">Smoking cessation</span> is always indicated{% endif %}

{% if answers.dose_smokes < 1 and answers.dose_fev1 < 1 and answers.dose_exacerbations < 1 and answers.dose_mrc < 1 %} No specific recommendations can be made on the basis of the Dose index of this patient. {% endif %}
